title: You All Over Me (Taylor's Version)
description:
It's been a long and fun journey but we have finally gotten to the vault songs! We kick it off by breaking down You All Over Me featuring Maren Morris! Who is she talking about in this song? Why did she keep so many great songs from us for so long?
And a big thank you to our boy Raphael for sending us such a thoughtful gift!
What did we miss? What album should we break down next? Let us know!
